### ============================================
### STEP-UP AUTHENTICATION - SEND CODE
### ============================================
###

### Send Code - Process Update Action
# @name sendCodeProcessUpdate
POST {{bevalk_base_url}}{{apiVersion}}/step-up/send-code
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "action": "process.update"
}

> {%
    client.log("Step-up code sent to email for process.update action");
%}

